1568
02:12:17,525 --> 02:12:25,350
that affect the installation of the primary use of the pole, residential concerns, and aesthetic considerations.

1569
02:12:26,111 --> 02:12:37,599
So those are all the reasons that the small cell committee has to take into consideration, and I'm happy to see residential concerns are on the list.

1570
02:12:38,899 --> 02:12:47,065
The city of Method is particularly sensitive to the visual impacts of small cell wireless infrastructures, therefore it shall implement and impose

1571
02:12:47,578 --> 02:13:12,970
on an interim basis, reasonable aesthetic standards pertaining to the size of the antenna, the equipment box, and or related cabling, placement of equipment on support structures, establishing flush mounting requirements and spacing requirements, and aesthetic measures such as paint matching or design matching for small wireless facilities in specific areas.

1572
02:13:13,944 --> 02:13:30,136
camouflage and other concealment methods, and for residential areas, guidelines on structures, heights and lengths, and minimum setbacks, rules for dwellings, parks, playgrounds, or similar recreational areas.

1573
02:13:30,956 --> 02:13:35,820
So I'm asking tonight, Mr. President, what are the minimum setback rules?

1574
02:13:36,420 --> 02:13:43,025
The policy does not talk about minimum setback rules for dwellings, parks, playgrounds,

1575
02:13:43,586 --> 02:13:46,148
or similar recreational areas.

1576
02:13:47,509 --> 02:14:05,842
And I call that out, Mr. President, because part of the reporting that Verizon has to do, part of the reporting package, and it's voluminous, there's a lot of requests, is that when they select a location, there has to be criteria why they selected that pole.

1577
02:14:06,522 --> 02:14:09,905
There's thousands of poles in the city, why did you select that pole?

1578
02:14:10,885 --> 02:14:17,554
And the one I pulled up from George Street, like I said, there were 44 applicants on that for all different locations.

1579
02:14:18,495 --> 02:14:21,479
The one I pulled up was the poll located at 50 George Street.

1580
02:14:22,187 --> 02:14:25,308
And Verizon came out with this as their selection criteria.

1581
02:14:25,908 --> 02:14:37,971
