1582
02:14:38,691 --> 02:14:41,131
The location itself is set in the public right of way.

1583
02:14:41,651 --> 02:14:44,372
This location was not only chosen for its compliance

1584
02:14:44,715 --> 02:15:03,060
with Verizon Wireless and National Grid requirements, but respect to the municipality's desire for co-locations on existing structures, and it is not directly adjacent to a park, school, or playground.

1585
02:15:05,761 --> 02:15:13,303
I might be mistaken, Mr. President, but our requirement says proximity to residential dwellings, school, parks, or playgrounds.

1586
02:15:14,027 --> 02:15:16,428
So they omitted residential dwellings.

1587
02:15:17,628 --> 02:15:17,948
Why?

1588
02:15:18,889 --> 02:15:35,895
Because many of these 44 poles, these new towers, are all within 20, 30 yards of bedrooms, dining rooms, kitchens, front yards, play areas next to homes, porches.

1589
02:15:37,575 --> 02:15:43,077
So I'm curious, Mr. President, I would offer this as an amendment

1590
02:15:45,002 --> 02:16:03,249
Why in the location selection criteria from Verizon, and I assume this is the case on all 44 applicants, but in particular for 50 George Street, why did they omit this as a chosen location and not include the proximity to residential dwellings?

1591
02:16:05,570 --> 02:16:09,391
So that's another amendment I'd like to add, Mr. President.

1592
02:16:10,071 --> 02:16:14,013
And that is missing from our criteria, which is in

1593
02:16:15,636 --> 02:16:16,676
our interim policy.

1594
02:16:18,397 --> 02:16:42,144
And that's an important criteria, Mr. President, because as I'll state a little further down, there are reports out there, and I have several of them in front of me, Mr. President, that talk about the potential exposure and the risk for pregnant women, children, elderly, individuals that may have implants,

1595
02:16:42,814 --> 02:16:47,717
or cardiac concerns, Mr. President, or neurological problems.

1596
02:16:48,198 --> 02:16:51,320
There may be concerns, Mr. President, with exposure.

1597
02:16:52,801 --> 02:17:10,833
And the fact, Mr. President, that 5G, much of the information over the last 20 years, a robust body of independent science has emerged showing significant biological impacts from exposure to radio frequency microwave radiation.

1598
02:17:11,382 --> 02:17:22,449
including clear evidence of cancer, neurological and cognitive harm, heart abnormalities, reproductive effects, and microwave sickness, Mr. President.

1599
02:17:23,790 --> 02:17:26,652
All affecting the individuals that I spoke about.

1600
02:17:27,772 --> 02:17:40,220
And human exposure guidelines for radio frequency microwave radiation used by the FCC are more than 20 years old and addressed only thermal,

1601
02:17:41,065 --> 02:17:43,206
not biological impacts of exposure.

1602
02:17:44,746 --> 02:17:49,187
So that also, Mr. President, is another concern that's out there.

1603
02:17:50,008 --> 02:18:01,691
And I raise this, Mr. President, on behalf of residents that may feel that their voice doesn't count, may feel that they don't have input on this and it's a done deal.

1604
02:18:02,531 --> 02:18:05,292
And I wanna raise awareness, Mr. President,

1605
02:18:05,730 --> 02:18:19,900
where many of these small cell towers will be located, like I said, within 20, 30, 40 yards of homes, bedrooms, porches, and where our families congregate, Mr. President.

1606
02:18:20,260 --> 02:18:22,501
