1642
02:23:03,943 --> 02:23:09,848
And I think we should do our due diligence prior to that, Mr. President.

1643
02:23:10,768 --> 02:23:19,215
And last but not least, and I appreciate my colleagues indulging me on this, but it is an important issue.

1644
02:23:19,295 --> 02:23:20,376
It's been around two years.

1645
02:23:20,816 --> 02:23:21,897
Now it's coming to a head.

1646
02:23:22,358 --> 02:23:23,739
Verizon put us on notice.

1647
